<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CFS :: FORM</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>CHAD FARMING SOLUTIONS</h2>
    <form action="" method="POST">
        <label for="townName">What is the name of your town?:</label><br>
        <input type="text" id="townName" name="townName" size="50" maxlength="50" required><br>

        <label for="season">What season are you currently in?:</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="seasonWet" name="season" value="Wet" required>
        <label for="seasonWet">Wet</label><br>
        <input type="radio" id="seasonDry" name="season" value="Dry">
        <label for="seasonDry">Dry</label><br>
        

        <p>What are the following environmental factors in your town during this season?</p>

        <label for="temperature">Average temperature of the soil:</label><br>
        <input type="text" pattern="\d*" id="temperature" name="temperature" min="0" max="100" size="3" maxlength="3" required>
        <label for="temperature">Â°C</label><br>

        <label for="rainfall">Average rainfall:</label><br>
        <input type="text" pattern="\d*" id="rainfall" name="rainfall" min="0" max="1000" size="4" maxlength="4" required>
        <label for="rainfall">mm</label><br>

        <label for="ph">Average pH of the soil:</label><br>
        <input type="text" pattern="\d*" id="ph" name="ph" min="0" max="14" size="2" maxlength="2" required><br>

        <p>Which of the following produce do you grow in your town?:</p>
        <label for="crop1">Crop 1</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop1" name="produce" value="Crop1"><br>
        <label for="crop2">Crop 2</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop2" name="produce" value="Crop2"><br>
        <label for="crop3">Crop 3</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop3" name="produce" value="Crop3"><br>
        <label for="crop4">Crop 4</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop4" name="produce" value="Crop4"><br>
        <label for="crop5">Crop 5</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop5" name="produce" value="Crop5"><br>
        <label for="crop6">Crop 6</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop6" name="produce" value="Crop6"><br>
        <label for="crop7">Crop 7</label>
        <input type="checkbox" id="crop7" name="produce" value="Crop7"><br>

        <input type="submit" value="Submit">
    </form>
</body>
</html>
